e $C^*$-algebras\n$\\mathcal{A}$, we determine precisely the centre of the bidual, namely,\n$Z({V_\\mathcal{A}}^{**})$ is Banach algebra isomorphic to $\\mathcal{A}^{**}\n\\otimes_{eh} \\mathcal{A}^{**}$, where $\\otimes_{eh}$ denotes the extended\nHaagerup tensor product.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 15 Sep 2018 21:37:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-18"}
