.0-m and 0.4-m DEV. In\nthe regression model analyzed from the aspect of satisfaction, the 2.32-Nm TOR\nand 0.27-m DEV are the optimal values. We expect our research on shared\nsteering control with an assistance system to be applied to the experience\ndesign of a lateral semi-autonomous vehicle.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 16 Sep 2018 13:14:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-18"}
